{"tid":1287104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每人10個蘋果account","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:48:47.000Z","uid":118219,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a75cad8d64e919c52fd28b4f3a2d99a2707eea06","tid":1287104,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:30:01.000Z","msg":"對於好多人講$3真係跌都跌咗<br />\n<br />\n如果有心幫蘋果不如整多幾個account課金？每人十個係基本！整多幾個藍尸fb ac, email都已經夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗緊會員人數越多應該會增加廣告商落廣告機會，嘩！蘋果有300萬會員喎！落個廣告有300萬人睇到！好抵！<br />\n<br />\n好多人話點解唔眾籌，好似立場咁比人任課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得蘋果咁大間報社佢都唔想比人知唔掂，唔掂既話都冇人係到落廣告啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然比錢方法蘋果都要再諗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！！！<br />\n每人10個Ac！30蚊唔係比唔到掛？"},{"pid":"0d0c073800b0b6e1499a71a2c0ab97c4b48278ed","tid":1287104,"uid":118219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講</code>"},{"pid":"6029b642f2a806d8bbf9f2db21ddb3adf7605603","tid":1287104,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"<code>我要見律師</code>"},{"pid":"676092d3015f2a1ccbd9278c38b7013382cdfd8b","tid":1287104,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"fbc21a264abdf7cfe84982416986d6eb7b92d469","tid":1287104,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講</code>到上熱門"},{"pid":"052de724bb666bfc3fa256e6aa0011da967a2758","tid":1287104,"uid":71216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"我無嘢好講"},{"pid":"820765c0ddc901a4b7cb55fea46734e0afa5c611","tid":1287104,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"支持